Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.086 --> 00:00:08.225
Namaste, I'm Lata Jain,
Welcome to Lata's Kitchen

00:00:08.225 --> 00:00:12.922
Black-eyed beans are very
nutritious and rich of protein

00:00:12.922 --> 00:00:16.974
Today I'm going to make Lobia
Chaat (Black eyed pea chaat)

00:00:16.974 --> 00:00:25.741
Its tasty as well as healthy, Lets see
the ingredients required for making it

00:00:25.742 --> 00:00:30.703
Black-eyed beans - 1/2 cup, 
soaked in water overnight

00:00:30.820 --> 00:00:32.887
Tomatoes -2, medium sized

00:00:32.887 --> 00:00:34.844
Potato - 1, boiled

00:00:34.844 --> 00:00:37.662
Cilantro - 2 tbsp, chopped

00:00:37.662 --> 00:00:40.002
Green Chillies - 2, finely chopped

00:00:40.002 --> 00:00:47.530
Sweet N Sour chutney - 3 tbsp, 
you can also use green chutney with one lemon juice

00:00:47.656 --> 00:00:50.207
Cumin Seeds - 1/4 tsp

00:00:50.207 --> 00:00:53.320
Chaat Masala - 1/2 tsp

00:00:53.370 --> 00:00:56.335
Red Chilly powder

00:00:56.335 --> 00:00:59.763
Baking Soda - 1/8 tsp

00:00:59.763 --> 00:01:03.164
Salt - 1 tsp, adjust to taste

00:01:03.214 --> 00:01:04.753
Water - 1 cup

00:01:04.753 --> 00:01:08.444
Lets start making lobia chaat

00:01:08.444 --> 00:01:16.055
First we need to boil black eyed beans

00:01:16.055 --> 00:01:31.016
Add black-eyed beans, 1/2 tsp salt,
baking soda and 1 cup of water in cooker

00:01:34.563 --> 00:01:40.367
Cover the lid, turn on the gas, 
cook on high heat till first whistle

00:01:40.393 --> 00:01:46.492
then turn heat to low
and cook for another 10 minutes

00:01:53.562 --> 00:02:01.727
Roast Cumin Seeds in a tadka pan

00:02:08.445 --> 00:02:16.633
It is done, take it out into a plate

00:02:19.008 --> 00:02:22.930
After first whistle, now turn gas to low

00:02:23.750 --> 00:02:33.719
Chop the boiled potato into small pieces

00:02:38.406 --> 00:02:41.933
Chop tomatoes into small pieces

00:02:48.023 --> 00:02:51.391
Its been 10 minutes, turn off the gas

00:02:51.391 --> 00:02:54.211
Tomatoes are also done

00:02:54.406 --> 00:02:59.727
Its pressure has released, open its lid

00:03:04.180 --> 00:03:09.961
black-eyed beans, take it out in a mixing bowl

00:03:19.703 --> 00:03:27.789
Add chopped tomatoes,
potatoes and green chillies

00:03:27.789 --> 00:03:32.407
Add roasted cumin seeds and chaat masala

00:03:38.281 --> 00:03:40.608
Add salt

00:03:42.945 --> 00:03:53.719
Add red chilly powder, you
can adjust it to your taste

00:03:53.719 --> 00:03:56.643
Add sweet n sour chutney

00:03:59.891 --> 00:04:07.524
You can watch chutney recipe in my video
"Sweet and Sour Dry Mango Chutney"

00:04:10.148 --> 00:04:13.571
Mix all the ingredients well

00:04:15.219 --> 00:04:18.466
Add cilantro

00:04:22.445 --> 00:04:26.135
Colorful Lobia Chaat is ready

00:04:26.703 --> 00:04:28.852
Lobia chaat is ready

00:04:28.852 --> 00:04:39.718
You can have it as breakfast or
as a side dish with lunch and dinner

00:04:39.828 --> 00:04:43.505
Thanks for watching Lobia Chaat

